  <brief_title>Algovita Post-Market Clinical Study: Spinal Cord Stimulation to Treat Chronic Pain</brief_title>
  <official_title>Real-world Evaluation of Outcome Data Under a Prospective, Observational, Post-Market Clinical Study, Using the Algovita SCS System to Treat Patients With Chronic Pain of the Trunk and/or Limbs Per the Applicable Indications for Use</official_title>
